<plot>On a business journey between two destinations, main character boards a train. As train takes off towards the next station, Spacely gets a surprise visitor. Stranger offers Spacely an opportunity of a lifetime for him, a chance to go to space. To take advantage of it he must get off at the next station and board the next train. Not knowing what to do, Spacely gets off just in case. While waiting for the train he is absorbed by memory replays of the three most important elements in his life: parents, friend and wife.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?399694</url></doc>
